Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.43,0:00:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找吧  收集梦想的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.57,0:00:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使无奈也能感受到此刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.62,0:00:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比外表看起来更单纯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.25,0:00:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却无法坦诚表达心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.12,0:00:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是把想说的话收藏在口袋里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.40,0:00:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今更不能说出幼稚的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.70,0:00:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好说时间能解决一切 却怕无人能懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.84,0:00:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天24小时我都相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.55,0:00:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注视着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.25,0:01:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这是司空见惯的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.23,0:01:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间总是嘲笑着匆匆而过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.33,0:01:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其执着回忆 不如寻找现在的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.37,0:01:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像和父亲一起住的村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.58,0:01:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝  要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.35,0:01:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.75,0:02:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第55话 石之花与七宝的初恋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.13,0:02:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  该不会是假情报吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.76,0:02:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种村落会有四魂碎片吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.33,0:02:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇也感受不到\N四魂碎片的气息吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.54,0:02:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  完全没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.37,0:02:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之还是散开来寻找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.62,0:02:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.95,0:02:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会\N想一个人去勾引女人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.49,0:02:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.96,0:02:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有妖怪的气息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你这种态度对吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.46,0:02:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.50,0:02:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.50,0:02:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明才刚开始找耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.97,0:03:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有妖怪的话一闻就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.88,0:03:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是想偷懒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.49,0:03:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪?七宝不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.59,0:03:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概跑去玩了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.19,0:03:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还是小孩子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.53,0:03:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  真是让人担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.54,0:03:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这阵子一直不断战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.57,0:03:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也该让他们两人独处一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.91,0:03:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.45,0:03:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会被你们逮到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.72,0:03:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.99,0:03:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揍扁她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.12,0:03:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.06,0:03:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你偷了我们家的柿子干对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有偷  你有看到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.36,0:03:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴  你这骗子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.53,0:03:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙  等哥哥回来后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.03,0:03:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会好好的修理你们一顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.80,0:04:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.54,0:04:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥不是早就死在战场上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.31,0:04:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我父亲在他死前照顾他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.38,0:04:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥才没有死呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.75,0:04:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浑蛋  小偷还敢打人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.76,0:04:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.33,0:04:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.27,0:04:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼…赢了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.28,0:04:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  狸猫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.85,0:04:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是狐狸啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是帮助我的谢礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.92,0:04:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要吃一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷来的柿子干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.86,0:04:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来真的是这家伙不对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好厉害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.53,0:05:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫五月  你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.00,0:05:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我叫做七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.17,0:05:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝?好帅气的名字呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.18,0:05:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲帮我取的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.04,0:05:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  你父亲是妖怪狸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狐狸啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.75,0:05:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是故意的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月  你有亲人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.82,0:05:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生后不久就去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.26,0:05:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我还有一个哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等他在战场立下大功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.70,0:05:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为武士后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.83,0:05:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会回来迎接我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那刚才那些小鬼在撒谎咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.64,0:05:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的哥哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.58,0:05:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定会回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.98,0:05:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.48,0:05:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也会活着回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.85,0:05:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别让你看看  我的宝贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要对它许愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.29,0:06:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何愿望都会实现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.23,0:06:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.49,0:06:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它叫做四魂碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.49,0:06:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是妖怪的宝贝碎片喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.86,0:06:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.01,0:06:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.88,0:06:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么愿望\N都能实现的四魂碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.38,0:06:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会成为武士的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.46,0:06:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥绝对不会说谎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.47,0:06:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗?法师大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.97,0:06:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家有妖怪盘踞着吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.91,0:06:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  若没有尽早驱除的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是法师的义务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.41,0:06:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不需要答谢我  名主大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.78,0:07:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说  各位的\N餐点与床铺已经准备好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.35,0:07:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒那家伙又在唬人了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.16,0:07:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.00,0:07:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.45,0:07:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有妖怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.58,0:07:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.09,0:07:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是胡扯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.19,0:07:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.89,0:07:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.83,0:07:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.20,0:07:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝你居然知道这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.33,0:07:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找这附近看起来最富裕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.53,0:07:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做法事的人家准没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.11,0:07:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总…总之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到四魂碎片了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.21,0:08:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是五月吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.49,0:08:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让姐姐看看你的碎片好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.36,0:08:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会想抢走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.99,0:08:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然要抢  如果是真的的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.53,0:08:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  坐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.37,0:08:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  只是看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.74,0:08:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  如果是真的四魂碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.41,0:08:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就非拿走不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.98,0:08:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来五月的愿望就会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.91,0:08:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会判断的这么草率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.58,0:08:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  笨蛋  我是大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.09,0:08:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.09,0:08:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了吧  我要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  路上小心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.46,0:08:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她回去好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.23,0:09:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月  你还是不想来我们家吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.94,0:09:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.24,0:09:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哥哥现正在回来的路上呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  那个碎片…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.14,0:09:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝  那是石之花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.95,0:09:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石之花?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.01,0:09:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是石英吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.02,0:09:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之是山上就能挖到的石头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不是四魂碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是冒牌货啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.76,0:09:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.26,0:09:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月是个可怜的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.27,0:09:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥已经确定是战死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.13,0:09:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她却不愿意相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.67,0:09:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望哥哥能快点回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.98,0:09:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我说由我们照顾她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.28,0:09:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她依然不肯离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.38,0:09:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经和哥哥一起生活的小屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.15,0:09:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然被轰出了名主的家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.92,0:09:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那小女孩可以利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.29,0:09:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我记住!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.31,0:10:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂拥有能创造\N奈落分身的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.51,0:10:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果向真正的碎片许愿的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.92,0:10:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月的哥哥就能活着回来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.85,0:10:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图形好可怕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.15,0:11:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.49,0:11:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.96,0:11:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉!你不是在睡觉吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.37,0:11:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放过我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.77,0:11:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是帮助人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.74,0:11:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别做梦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.87,0:11:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝  你也知道四魂之玉的可怕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.38,0:11:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是人类能使用的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.25,0:11:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  你为什么要偏袒那小女孩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷恋人家了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.99,0:11:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的脸长得蛮可爱的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.76,0:11:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  为了这么烂的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.59,0:11:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.03,0:11:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我迷恋她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.99,0:11:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在桔梗跟戈薇之间\N摇摆不定的你也没资格说我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.57,0:11:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去睡觉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.61,0:11:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.69,0:12:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.63,0:12:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.50,0:12:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了 你过得好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.64,0:12:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.64,0:12:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直相信!我一直相信着!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.54,0:12:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥一定会回来的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.15,0:12:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少应该向她道别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.19,0:12:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月会不会一直\N对着假碎片祈祷呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.73,0:12:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我实在说不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.03,0:12:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情的真相…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.17,0:12:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.47,0:12:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的愿望实现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.57,0:12:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.68,0:13:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉  七宝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.68,0:13:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那叫做五月的女孩那边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.99,0:13:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他真的很担心她呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.49,0:13:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月的哥哥早就不在人世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.19,0:13:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她却深信假的碎片而等待着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.90,0:13:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又要多管闲事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.37,0:13:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  虽然哥哥受了一点伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.01,0:13:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥真的回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.21,0:13:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.41,0:13:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是托你和四魂碎片的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.66,0:13:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!妖怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.03,0:13:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥要快点治好伤口\N恢复精神喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.90,0:14:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…让你吃了这么多苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.64,0:14:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后哥哥会让你很幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.61,0:14:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.01,0:14:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你过来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.42,0:14:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在名主家借宿的\N那一行人的伙伴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.45,0:14:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月  快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.62,0:14:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.29,0:14:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能把那东西拿来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.56,0:14:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的四魂碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.20,0:14:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开五月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么  哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.57,0:14:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂碎片的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.44,0:14:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不就有一个吗  你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.27,0:14:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不明白啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.87,0:14:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种烂石头一点用都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.21,0:14:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然将实现五月愿望的碎片…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.69,0:14:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  矮子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.19,0:14:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拿四魂碎片来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.46,0:14:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我就扭断五月的脖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.50,0:15:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是你哥哥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现出原形吧  妖怪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.20,0:15:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狐火!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.47,0:15:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小鬼真狠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.71,0:15:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来觉得当她哥哥也不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.31,0:15:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.31,0:15:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浑蛋  我饶不了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.49,0:15:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月  快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.27,0:15:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.91,0:15:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经被发现了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.41,0:15:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.78,0:15:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月  你先逃走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.42,0:16:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我怎么能这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.22,0:16:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只能一个人骑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.66,0:16:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.63,0:16:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.34,0:16:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是五月住的小木屋吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.55,0:16:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看  是大肚子妖怪的杰作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少他们似乎是逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.89,0:16:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  弥勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.19,0:16:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先追上七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.06,0:16:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两人一定要平安啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是七宝的狐妖术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.57,0:16:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是五月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.58,0:16:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起  云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.98,0:17:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝在妖怪那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.92,0:17:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  走吧  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.72,0:17:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月  你一定要平安逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.00,0:17:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小女孩逃走是没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.17,0:17:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.31,0:17:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矮子  我要拿你当人质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.31,0:17:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去抢四魂碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.04,0:17:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你一开始就应该找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.31,0:17:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还刻意践踏五月的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.02,0:17:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浑蛋  我饶不了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.25,0:17:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思  你想和我打吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.79,0:17:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.46,0:17:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招  消化液
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.60,0:17:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.90,0:17:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招  爆雷筒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.60,0:17:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.57,0:18:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子  你闹够了没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.05,0:18:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量还是不够吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.72,0:18:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能跟大家一样战斗吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.60,0:18:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.57,0:18:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  还没得到教训
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.88,0:18:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又变成奇怪的家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.08,0:18:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭家伙  你在找碴吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.82,0:18:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.36,0:18:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你试试刚领悟的爆流破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.16,0:18:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子  你在胡说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.07,0:19:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将对手的妖气卷入风之伤中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.64,0:19:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让妖气逆流的必杀剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.11,0:19:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆流…啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.65,0:19:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!对手的妖气太弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.65,0:19:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆流破根本就用不出来嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.65,0:19:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在罗哩叭唆什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.92,0:19:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.66,0:19:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.79,0:19:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.93,0:19:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是昨晚从名主家中\N赶走的妖怪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.44,0:19:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.68,0:19:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝  你这次相当努力嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.92,0:19:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.45,0:19:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.95,0:19:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.42,0:19:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你解决了那只妖怪对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.66,0:20:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我  是犬夜叉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.17,0:20:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪就已经被扁得很惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.20,0:20:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.64,0:20:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只妖怪知道打不过我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.87,0:20:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想利用五月吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.68,0:20:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一牵扯到四魂碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.48,0:20:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会遭遇不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.45,0:20:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我忘的一干二净
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.48,0:20:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才让五月碰到这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.49,0:20:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月  对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.16,0:20:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.50,0:20:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.77,0:20:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要让名主大人照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.97,0:20:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我已经知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.74,0:20:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥已经不在人世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.89,0:21:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重喔  五月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.72,0:21:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.26,0:21:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能遇见你真的太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.60,0:21:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五月  你一定要幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.03,0:21:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你一样没有父母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.41,0:21:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我不是一个人活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.12,0:21:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝  你是不是喜欢那孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.49,0:21:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.06,0:21:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是人小鬼大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.56,0:21:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然小也是男人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.23,0:21:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初恋呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.57,0:21:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝  走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.84,0:21:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝  再拖拖拉拉就不理你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.44,0:21:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.33,0:22:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了真正重要的事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.64,0:22:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能舍弃其他一切就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.92,0:22:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而现实却是残酷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.40,0:22:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这样的时刻只要随时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.37,0:22:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.94,0:23:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑海浮现你的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.65,0:23:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-但愿直到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.69,0:23:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远沉睡的那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.89,0:23:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿你的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.90,0:23:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不止息存在我心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.05,0:23:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个村子里的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.59,0:23:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都被妖怪公主魅惑\N而一去不回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.66,0:23:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然弥勒法师\N单枪匹马前去驱逐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.96,0:23:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是提到弥勒法师的弱点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.96,0:23:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是美丽的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.83,0:23:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子就有点危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.83,0:24:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然担心他的珊瑚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.10,0:24:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也跟随着一同前往…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.67,0:24:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座山里有着悲伤的传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.34,0:24:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.84,0:24:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷雾深处的美女诱惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.88,0:24:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待



